20#include "config.h"
21#include "system.h"
22#include "coretypes.h"
23#include "tm.h"
24#include "tree.h"
25#include "varasm.h"
26#include "netbsd-protos.h"
27
28static void
29netbsd_patch_builtin (enum built_in_function fncode)
30{
31 tree fn = builtin_decl_explicit (fncode);
32 tree sym;
33 char *newname;
34
35 if (!fn)
36 return;
37
38 sym = DECL_ASSEMBLER_NAME (fn);
39 newname = ACONCAT (("__c99_", IDENTIFIER_POINTER (sym), NULL));
40
41 set_user_assembler_name (fn, newname);
42
43 fn = builtin_decl_implicit (fncode);
44 if (fn)
45 set_user_assembler_name (fn, newname);
46}
47
48void
49netbsd_patch_builtins (void)
50{
51 netbsd_patch_builtin (BUILT_IN_CABSF);
52 netbsd_patch_builtin (BUILT_IN_CABS);
53 netbsd_patch_builtin (BUILT_IN_CABSL);
54}
